        { text: "Navigate through all 4 memory slots in sequence. Feel the tempo change automatically with each slot load. This IS your set list — each memory is a song at its own tempo, and the transitions happen instantly.", why: "A DJ plans energy flow across a set — slow build, peak, cooldown, peak again. Your memory slots do the same thing. The tempo arc across a set is what keeps an audience engaged for 30-60 minutes." }
